Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Four more months, four more months, four more months!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I bet you're excited, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. I, uh, I could be excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't really know. I wasn't really think…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, you gotta be excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.62,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I guess maybe I'm a little kinda sort of excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:30.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So, um, why am I excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:36.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Because the next Daring Do book is coming out exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,four months from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's how exciting it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:43.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, what amazing, incredible, awesome adventure do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Daring Do will have in her next book, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Will she at long last stalk the Fortress of Talikon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:53.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Only to be forced to contend with its dreaded and impenetrable arrow defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:58.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And if so, could her skill, quick wits, and courage possibly carry the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:03.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Or will her next adventure bring her face to face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,with the vast and horrible Ahuizotl himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:12.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whould she cover? Turn tail and run?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:16.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Or would she fly at him, full bore, knowing full well against all odds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:21.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,that the greatest challenge she ever faced was still sure be no match for…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:23.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ah, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:30.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm not so sure she's gonna last another four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:12.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Three months and twenty six days. Three months and twenty six days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Three months and twenty six days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Heya, Twilight, aren't you excited…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So glad you've finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,W-what's everypony doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're having a holyday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, what holyday would today be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,National Random Holyday Party Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of it ether, but punch is quite tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You might say the secret ingridient is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,{\i1}А SECRET!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How come nopony bothered to invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I came to invite you personaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:53.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But it seems you were a speck too busy reading the last Daring Do book for the twelfth time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, in three months and twenty six more days I'll be able to read the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:02.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, haven't you heard? Тhe release of the next book got pushed another two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Two more months?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting so long already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:12.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can take another two months! I'll never make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can vouch for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Did they give a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The publisher just said author A.K. Yearling won't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to finish the book for another two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How could you possibly know that before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I am the series' biggest fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I am just as big a fan as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:35.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm the one who first introduced you to the books, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling just might be my favorite author.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know everything about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:45.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where she grew up, where she studied literature, where she wrote the first Daring Do book…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Where she lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:51.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Eeeeh, no… Though I could probably find out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The new book is obviously delayed because she needs help dealing with whatever everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:02.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,nonsense is distracting her from spending her every living breathing second writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:07.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So I.. I mean, fans like me can get to read the next book ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:13.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Think about it, we could help her with her laundry, buy her groceries, cooking her meals, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now, who wouldn't appreciate that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hm… I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What she probably wants most of all is respect for her privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She can always just say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, how's about getting that address?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:55.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why would she live in this remote part of Equestria except to keep folks from intruding on her privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We should respect…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:05:00.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think I spotted the house! We're super close! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:11.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Apparently somepony has intruded on her privacy pretty hard already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How-ly, somepony really trashed this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.47,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,O-or…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:30.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Maybe A. K. Yearling is a terrible, horrible, unbelieavable slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I hope A.K. Yearling's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What if something terrible happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know! There might be no more books!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, but of course I'd be worried about her… too…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.89,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:51.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A. K. Year-ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,W-we didn't do this, we swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.67,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,What have you done to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We didn't do this, Miss Yearling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're awfully glad to see you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ok, clearly this isn't the best time, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I just got to say, how much we all really love your books!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.09,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,It's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Great! Maybe now would be a good time for me to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,how we can help move the new book along a little faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, a minute, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling has made it pretty clear that she wants to be left alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We need to respect her wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You should tell that to those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling is Daring Do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling is Daring Do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A. K. Yearling and Daring Do are one and the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My mind is officially blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ah, come on. I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow, so much action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.21,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Daring Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:25.01,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,As you've probably surmised, our earlier search for this treasure was… unsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.93,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,So kind of you to find it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.98,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Give it back, Cabaleron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.49,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,That's Doctor Cabaleron to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He's from book four. {\i1}"Daring Do and Eraser of Dreams."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He wanted to partner with Daring Do on her adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know! But she refused. I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The real Daring Do and the real Cabaleron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:49.04,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,So let me guess, Ahuizotl has put you up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:53.21,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,You're stealing the ring to give to him, so his hold on the fortress of Talikon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:56.01,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,will be good for eight centuries as foretold by prophesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.59,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,Close, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:04.83,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sell this to him, make a bundle and retire from archaeology in splendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:11.74,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Cabaleron, you fool! You're dooming the valley to eight centuries of unrelenting heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.63,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,To market, henchponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Should we go in and help her, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.96,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She was just trying to help, Miss Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:35.38,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Daring Do doesn't need help. She handles her business herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We've gotta go help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:44.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You heard her. She says she works alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How can we just stand by and do nothing? You know what's at stake here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:51.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ahuizotl has sought control of the Tenochtitlan Basin since book three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:56.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,True. But in book four, she defeated Ahuizotl, and secured control of the Amulet of Atonement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:02.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,dispelling the dark magic of the Quetzalcoatl Empress, and thus protecting the basin with the Radiant Shield of Rasdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:06.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But the Radiant Shield of Razdon is vulnerable to the dark enchantment of the rings of Scorched Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But are you forgetting that the Rings were scattered to the four corners of Tenochtitlan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,thus rendering the dark enchantment powerless?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Only if you assume that the Rings have yet to be retrieved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and the ring Cabaleron just stole isn't the last to completely restore the dark tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and its cruel hold on the Tenaktitlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Did you ever think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:25.22,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You gotta admit, Rainbow Dash makes a pretty good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:29.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We gotta help Daring Do retrieve the ring for safekeep before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:34.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay. But sounds to me like we're in way-way-way over our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:37.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're going to need a carefully thought-out plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's not a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.31,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:55.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,To join in adventure with the greatest, bravest, coolest, most incredible hero I can ever…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe I just need a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just another adventure. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Though, doing it alongside Daring Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:19.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can get a picture taken with her! Or an autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's just a pony like any other pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:29.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A pony who stops entire armies of bad guys with nothing more than her bare hoofs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and an attitude, and!..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's starting to hurt…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.03,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Oh. It's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:52.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Think fast. This is your big chance to impress her with your quick wit and courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:03.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I am su-u-uch a huge fan…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait! Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:13.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I promise I could be a huge, huge help if you just give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.39,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.26,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.34,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But why won't you let me team up with you, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.38,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,My work always involves secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.50,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,and since you never know who you can trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.10,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,it's best never to trust anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:31.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But just because you can't trust some doesn't mean nopony can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.18,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't have time to argue…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Neither do I. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.69,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm even talking to her…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Looks like they decided to have an early dinner before making their way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,back down the hill to the marketplace in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're gonna ambush them like you did in book four, the Huravian Caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Or maybe that neat trick you did in book three,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:05.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,where you swoop in and knock three guys down with one swing! Or maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just watching very quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of ambush are you gonna use then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.85,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I've been led to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:29.22,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,you have in your possession an item of significant importance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.81,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,that might be for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.71,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.69,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,I did have another buyer lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:39.59,CABALERON,,0,0,0,,but he's not here. So, sounds like we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.53,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Ahuizotl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Be cool, Rainbow Dash, be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:01.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The ring, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.77,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Now, Ahuizotl, you know I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.72,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,but I can't give you the ring till I properly proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.03,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:22.03,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Because my friends here have a proposal of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.40,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, Daring Do… Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:57.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Daring Do! I've got your hat! Want me to toss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Daring Do! Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Daring Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll come help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.52,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.81,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I'd say you've already helped plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What have I done…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness you're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Quick. Where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:43.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Daring Do and the ring have been captured by the dreaded Ahuizotl,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Dash, I'm sure whatever you did was an honest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We can't go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looks a mite like she needs our help more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Trying to help is how I got in this mess in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You were right, Twilight. We should have stayed out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look. There's more going on here than meets the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,In every Daring Do book there always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We can't turn our backs on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want my help, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Perhaps. But she might need it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No. My hero's way better off without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This doesn't sound like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Where's the Rainbow Dash who would help anypony at the drop of the hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or pith helmet, as the case may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's here where she's got no business being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She should be at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's fine to look up to Daring Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you put her so high up on the pedestal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you can't even see your own worth anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's in the fortress, and we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And we wouldn't be who we are if we didn't go in after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And neither would you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, are you with us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.70,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Surrender now, Ahuizotl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.08,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Or I'll be forced to take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:26.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daring Do! I will so miss your amusing laughter jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:29.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Now I must leave to commense the ring-placing ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:36.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to unleash eight hundred years of unrelenting sweltering heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You can flap too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:21.13,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I was just about to save myself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:24.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Of course. I just thought you might need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.27,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Have I mentioned yet that I work alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Have I mentioned yet that you're lucky I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Drop the ring, Ahui…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,whatever your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Pass the ring, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:02.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:19.72,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.46,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Help me get all these rings off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:39.11,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,If we can remove the giant ring at the bottom, the whole fort will collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Was this your plan all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.83,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I had to find a way to get into the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You did that on purpose? But… but I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.31,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I didn't count on how heavy these rings would be though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:54.17,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I guess having little help can be handy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.71,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,You could flap too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:21.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ponies, run! This place is going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:41.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Daring Do! I will have my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.78,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I'd never have done this without you, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.54,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I've got a book to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:00.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just had the coolest adventure with the coolest pony ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Came this close to blowing it because I got wrapped up in how awesome she was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:06.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot about how awesome I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Good thing I didn't, cause it gave me a chance to show her how important it is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,to put your trust in somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Package from A.K. Yearling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:23.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sweet! A new book a week before anypony else gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ohmygoshohmygoshohmygoshohmygosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
